headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Tesla Stock Soars on Driving-Assistance Plans in China
summary: The S&P 500 jumped 1.8% on Monday, March 24, as investors reacted to reports that imminent reciprocal tariffs could exclude levies on key sectors.
